2015年7月，公司宣佈飛行測試計劃因國内貨幣貶值與政府削減開支而延後兩年，不過第二次試飛仍於10月26日在Gavião Peixoto進行。<ref name="AINonline8Nov2015EmbraersKC-390ReturnsToFlightTest">{{cite news |last1=Carey |first1=Bill |title=Embraer's KC-390 Returns to Flight Test |url=http://www.ainonline.com/aviation-news/defense/2015-11-08/embraers-kc-390-returns-flight-test |access-date=2016-03-22 |publisher=AINonline |date=2015-11-08 |archive-date=2016-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330024756/http://www.ainonline.com/aviation-news/defense/2015-11-08/embraers-kc-390-returns-flight-test |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Trimble|first1=Stephen|title=Embraer announces two-year delay for KC-390|url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/embraer-announces-two-year-delay-for-kc-390-415195/|work=[[Flightglobal|Flightglobal]]|date=2015-07-30|accessdate=2021-10-17|archive-date=2018-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219104525/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/embraer-announces-two-year-delay-for-kc-390-415195/|dead-url=no}}</ref>到

2016年2月，首架原型機的飛行時間已超過100小時。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/21602/KC-390-ja-ultrapassou-a-marca-de-100-horas-de-voo/ |title=KC-390 já ultrapassou a marca de 100 horas de voo |date=2016-02-18 |publisher=Defesanet |language=pt |access-date=2021-10-17 |archive-date=2016-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424083204/http://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/21602/KC-390-ja-ultrapassou-a-marca-de-100-horas-de-voo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨著試飛的恢復，製造商預計在2017年對該飛機進行正式的認證，並爭取在2018年開始交付該飛機。在試飛的八個月時間内，kc-390進行了地面振動測試來驗證氣動彈性模型以及對任務，[[航空電子|航空電子]]，[[起落架|起落架]]，[[电子飞行仪表系统|电子飞行仪表系统]]和[[飞行控制系统|飞行控制系统]]的測試。巴西航空工業公司爲了報告良好的測試可動性，有時會一天進行兩次飛行。飛機也在速度，馬赫數和高度以及所有縫翼，襟翼和起落架位置的限制條件下進行了測試。<ref name="AINonline17Feb2016EmbraersKC-390ReturnsToFlightTest">{{cite news |last1=Alcock |first1=Charles |title=Embraer's KC-390 Returns to Flight Test |url=http://www.ainonline.com/aviation-news/defense/2016-02-17/embraers-kc-390-returns-flight-test |publisher=AINonline |date=2016-02-17 |access-date=2016-03-22 |archive-date=2016-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321110521/http://www.ainonline.com/aviation-news/defense/2016-02-17/embraers-kc-390-returns-flight-test |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第二架原型機（PT-ZNJ)於2016年3月製成，並於4月28日首飛。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/21833/Embraer-conclui-o-segundo-prototipo-do-cargueiro-militar-KC-390/ |title=Embraer conclui o segundo protótipo do cargueiro militar KC-390 |date=2016-03-15 |publisher=Defesanet |language=pt |access-date=2021-10-17 |archive-date=2016-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419010231/http://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/21833/Embraer-conclui-o-segundo-prototipo-do-cargueiro-militar-KC-390 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.kc-390.com/documents/Progress-Report-01-KC-390.pdf |title= KC-390's Flight Test Campaign Progresses |publisher= Embraer Defense & Security |access-date= 2016-07-14 |archive-date= 2016-09-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160921221313/http://www.kc-390.com/documents/Progress-Report-01-KC-390.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |url= http://www.kc-390.com/ |title= KC-390 Flight Campaign Status |year= 2016 |medium= Motion picture |publisher= Embraer Defense & Security |access-date= 2021-10-17 |archive-date= 2016-08-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160806135109/http://kc-390.com/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>届時，Richard Aboulafia的Teal集團估計C-390的單價爲5000到5500萬美元，這比大力神運輸機少了1500萬美元。<ref name=CNN20jul2017>{{cite news |url= https://money.cnn.com/2017/07/20/news/companies/embraer-kc390-military-transport-lockheed-c130-super-hercules/index.html |title= Brazilian aircraft takes on an American military icon |author= Thom Patterson |work= [[CNNMoney|CNNMoney]] |date= 2017-07-20 |accessdate= 2021-10-17 |archive-date= 2018-10-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181022073644/https://money.cnn.com/2017/07/20/news/companies/embraer-kc390-military-transport-lockheed-c130-super-hercules/index.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>

