==运营历史==

'''巴西'''

2014年，巴西政府訂購了28架KC-390，旨在逐步取代巴西空軍的貨運機隊，包括其他C-130。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aerotime.aero/clement.charpentreau/23905-embraer-delivers-first-kc-390-to-the-brazilian-air-force|title=Embraer delivers first KC-390 to the brazilian air force|website=aerotime.aero|date=2019-09-05|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203144824/https://www.aerotime.aero/clement.charpentreau/23905-embraer-delivers-first-kc-390-to-the-brazilian-air-force|dead-url=no}}</ref>第一家KC-390於2019年9月4日正式交付給巴西空軍。<ref name=flight4sep2019>{{cite news |url= https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/brazilian-air-force-receives-first-embraer-kc-390-460668/ |title= Brazilian air force receives first Embraer KC-390 |date= 2019-09-04 |author= Garrett Reim |work= Flightglobal |accessdate= 2021-10-17 |archive-date= 2019-09-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190915131159/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/brazilian-air-force-receives-first-embraer-kc-390-460668/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>KC-390第一部隊運輸集團(1º GTT)''ZEUS''在Anápolis空軍基地服役。<ref name="Anapolis">{{cite web|url=https://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/39147/KC-390---FAB-recebe-quarta-aeronave-KC-390-Millennium/|title=KC-390 - FAB recebe quarta aeronave KC-390 Millennium|date=2020-12-20|website=Defesanet|access-date=2021-04-13|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017081851/https://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/39147/KC-390---FAB-recebe-quarta-aeronave-KC-390-Millennium/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

 

2021年1月，在第二次[[COVID-19_大流行|COVID-19 大流行]]期間，位於亞馬遜熱帶雨林的巴西城市[[瑪瑙斯|瑪瑙斯]]的醫療負擔過重，需要醫療資源和轉移患者。巴西空軍發起了一項重大行動，動員了所有可用的運輸航空。C-390在這次行動中起了關鍵作用，執行了瑪瑙斯市與該國其他地區鏈接起來的空運任務，運送了各種醫療物資，並從已經醫療負荷過載的瑪瑙斯運送了數百位患者。<ref>{{cite web | url= https://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/39307/KC-390-transporta-mais-de-8-toneladas-de-equipamentos-para-Manaus/ | title= KC-390 transports more than 8 tons of equipment to Manaus | website= defesanet.com.br | date= 2021-01-14 | access-date= 2020-01-29 | archive-date= 2021-10-17 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211017081850/https://www.defesanet.com.br/kc390/noticia/39307/KC-390-transporta-mais-de-8-toneladas-de-equipamentos-para-Manaus/ | dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.aeroin.net/kc-390-voa-em-nova-missao-contra-a-crise-da-covid-19-em-manaus/|title=KC-390 flies on a new mission against the COVID-19 crisis in Manaus|date=2021-01-14|website=Aeroin.net|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019131408/https://www.aeroin.net/kc-390-voa-em-nova-missao-contra-a-crise-da-covid-19-em-manaus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''匈牙利'''

2020年11月17日，在[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]退役最後一架蘇聯時代的[[AN-26|AN-26]]軍用貨機接近六個月后，巴西航空工業公司宣佈與匈牙利簽訂了兩架KC-390的訂單，以及相關的培訓，支援和維護。第一架飛機將在2023年交付給匈牙利空軍，第二架則將於2024年交付。匈牙利國防軍訂購的配置包括[[重症監護室|重症監護室]]（ICU）套件，使匈牙利能夠在國外的人道主義任務中提供重症監護能力。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://embraer.com/global/en/news?slug=1206809-hungary-signs-contract-for-acquisition-of-two-multi-mission-kc-390-millennium-airlifters|title=Hungary Signs Contract For Acquisition of Two Multi-Mission KC-390 Millennium Airlifters|website=embraer.com|date=2020-11-17|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017081852/https://embraer.com/global/en/news?slug=1206809-hungary-signs-contract-for-acquisition-of-two-multi-mission-kc-390-millennium-airlifters|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''葡萄牙'''

2019年，巴西航空工業公司向葡萄牙國防部建議提供使用C-390作爲葡萄牙空軍老化的C-130機隊的替代方案。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://sol.sapo.pt/PaginaInicial/Sociedade/Interior.aspx?content_id=163719 |publisher=Sol |title=Reequipamento das FA: Portugal pondera comprar avião militar brasileiro |date=2010-02-23 }}{{dead link |date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes}}</ref> 2011年12月，葡萄牙政府將與巴西航空工業公司簽署一份價值8700萬歐元的合同，用於生產部分C-390。.<ref>{{cite news |title=Governo assina amanhã contrato com Embraer |url=https://economico.sapo.pt/noticias/governo-assina-amanha-contrato-com-embraer_133604.html |publisher=Diário Económico |date=2011-12-13 |url-status=dead|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120708035322/http://economico.sapo.pt/noticias/governo-assina-amanha-contrato-com-embraer_133604.html |archive-date=2012-07-08}}</ref>

2017年，葡萄牙政府授權購買五架C-390軍用飛機，並允許選擇性購買第六架。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://observador.pt/2017/07/27/governo-autoriza-compra-de-cinco-aeronaves-militares-kc-390-tambem-para-combater-incendios/ |title=Governo autoriza compra de cinco aeronaves militares KC-390 também para combater incêndios |author=Agência Lusa |website=Observador |date=2017-07-27 |access-date=2021-10-17 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019115846/https://observador.pt/2017/07/27/governo-autoriza-compra-de-cinco-aeronaves-militares-kc-390-tambem-para-combater-incendios/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最終葡萄牙軍隊將花費8.27億歐元購買5架C-390以及用於飛行員培訓的飛行模擬器。首架飛機將於2023年2月交付，交付計劃預計於2027年2月完成。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.reuters.com/article/us-portugal-embraer-military-idUSKCN1U61Q6 |title= Portugal to buy five Embraer military planes for 827 million euros |date= 2019-07-11 |work= Reuters |accessdate= 2021-10-17 |archive-date= 2021-10-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211019131408/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-portugal-embraer-military-idUSKCN1U61Q6 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

===營銷和订货===

C-390作爲噴氣動力替代洛克希德馬丁公司生產的C-130為目標進行銷售。截至2020年12月，巴西，葡萄牙和匈牙利共簽署了35架C-390的訂單，另有四個國家（阿根廷，智利，哥倫比亞和捷克共和國）表示有興趣采購該飛機。<ref name="FlightglobalEmbraerExpectsFirstOperational">{{cite news |last1=Trimble |first1=Stephen |title=Embraer expects first operational KC-390 buyer in 2014 |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/laad-embraer-expects-first-operational-kc-390-buyer-in-384442/ |work=[[Flightglobal|Flightglobal]] |date=2013-04-10 |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306163635/https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/laad-embraer-expects-first-operational-kc-390-buyer-in-384442/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

据报道，2007年，巴西邮政[[Correios|Correios]]有意购买至少5和飞机的最终20至25日，以代替使用商业货运服务的邮件运输。<ref>http://www.monitormercantil.com.br/imprimir_noticia.asp?id2=44595 {{Wayback|url=http://www.monitormercantil.com.br/imprimir_noticia.asp?id2=44595 |date=20071214092757 }} Costa confirma projeto dos Correios com cargueiro C-390]. Monitor Mercantil. 28 August 2007. Retrieved 15 October 2007.</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2007/09/04/216557/brazilian-postal-service-may-order-embraer-c-390-freighters.html|title=Brazilian postal service may order Embraer C-390 freighters|publisher=Flightglobal.com|date=2007-09-04|accessdate=2011-12-13|archive-date=2007-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071031030043/http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2007/09/04/216557/brazilian-postal-service-may-order-embraer-c-390-freighters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2011年5月19日，Correios将购买大约15架巴西航空工業公司的飛機。<ref>[http://oglobo.globo.com/economia/correios-investirao-ate-1-bi-para-criar-aerea-com-avioes-da-embraer-2767766 "Correios investirão até R$ 1 bi para criar aérea com aviões da Embraer" (in Portuguese).] {{Wayback|url=http://oglobo.globo.com/economia/correios-investirao-ate-1-bi-para-criar-aerea-com-avioes-da-embraer-2767766 |date=20140512031957 }} ''O Globo,'' 19 May 2011. Retrieved: 12 March 2012.</ref>

在2008年9月，[[葡萄牙空军|葡萄牙空军]]首席员工，在接受国家航空报社起飞的采訪中透露，在飞机作为一个可能的C-130机队更换服务的兴趣，尽管这种兴趣被概括为POAF正在密切关注在C-390的开发。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aeropress.pt/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=599 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-05-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081021104138/http://www.aeropress.pt/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=599 |archivedate=2008-10-21 }}</ref>在2010年2月，进一步通知，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sol.sapo.pt/PaginaInicial/Sociedade/Interior.aspx?content_id=163719|publisher=Sol|title=Reequipamento das FA: Portugal pondera comprar avião militar brasileiro|date=2010-02-23|accessdate=2011-12-13}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 报告说，巴西航空工业公司建议葡萄牙国防部收购KC-390，以替代老化的C-130。 

2011年12月宣布，葡萄牙政府将用于生产的KC-390的一部分，签订巴西航空工业公司的8千7百万欧元合同。<ref>{{cite news|title=Governo assina amanhã contrato com Embraer|url=http://economico.sapo.pt/noticias/governo-assina-amanha-contrato-com-embraer_133604.html|publisher=Diário Económico|date=2011-12-13|accessdate=2014-10-26|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017231825/http://jornaleconomico.sapo.pt/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年9月7日，法国有意购买10架KC-390巴西购买[[阵风战斗机|阵风战斗机]]谈判的一部分。。<ref>[http://www.estadao.com.br/noticias/nacional,negociacao-de-cacas-franceses-preve-venda-de-jato-da-embraer,430878,0.htm "Negociação de caças franceses prevê venda de jato da Embraer" (in Porguguese).] {{Wayback|url=http://www.estadao.com.br/noticias/nacional,negociacao-de-cacas-franceses-preve-venda-de-jato-da-embraer,430878,0.htm |date=20100315014659 }} ''Estadão,'' 7 September 2009. Retrieved: 2 May 2012.</ref>

于2009年10月2日，瑞典宣布，它將评估KC-390运输机在长期战术空运中的需求與F-X2报价的差距。[[JAS_39|JAS 39]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.defencetalk.com/saab-offers-gripen-fighter-technology-transfer-to-brazil-22389/|title=Saab Delivers the Perfect Match to Brazil|publisher=Defence Talk|date=2009-10-06|accessdate=2011-12-13|archive-date=2011-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111215154201/http://www.defencetalk.com/saab-offers-gripen-fighter-technology-transfer-to-brazil-22389/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年7月，[[巴西空军|巴西空军]]宣布，它將购买28架飞机。<ref>[http://economia.estadao.com.br/noticias/economia,fab-anuncia-intencao-de-comprar-28-avioes-kc-390-da-embraer,28339,0.htm "FAB anuncia intenção de comprar 28 aviões KC 390 da Embraer" (in Portuguese).] {{Wayback|url=http://economia.estadao.com.br/noticias/economia,fab-anuncia-intencao-de-comprar-28-avioes-kc-390-da-embraer,28339,0.htm |date=20191017231833 }}. ''Estadão,'' 21 July 2010. Retrieved: 14 March 2012.</ref>

在2010年8月，智利空军计划订购6架KC-390。<ref name=Chile_May_Tie/>9月，哥伦比亚打算订购12架KC-390。<ref name=Colombia_formalises_interest/>  同個月，有报道稱呼，捷克共和国空军可能购买两架KC-390。<ref name=Czech_KC-390s>{{cite web |url=http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2010/09/14/347288/czech-republic-outlines-need-for-two-kc-390s.html |title=Czech Republic outlines need for two KC-390s |accessdate=2010-09-15 |archive-date=2010-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918001107/http://www.flightglobal.com/articles/2010/09/14/347288/czech-republic-outlines-need-for-two-kc-390s.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

