有报道稱，巴西和阿联酋进行谈判以达成协议的军事合作，这一談判将涉及到十月下旬對KC-390的銷售。<ref name=gulfnews>[http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/uae/government/uae-and-brazil-to-sign-defence-agreement-1.686015 "UAE and Brazil to sign defence agreement".] {{Wayback|url=http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/uae/government/uae-and-brazil-to-sign-defence-agreement-1.686015 |date=20130730162512 }} ''Gulf News,'' 23 September 2010. Retrieved: 30 May 2012.</ref>

